title: Attomica - Complete Album Discography (1987-2012) [FLAC]
description:
This torrent contains the complete album discography of Brazilian thrash metal unit "Attomica".

Everything from their 1987 self-titled debut up to their 2012 release "Attomica IV" is included, all encoded in glorious lossless quality.

Fans of thrash metal will surely enjoy the albums contained in here and will most definitely be prone to adding them to their own album collections.
